Frontier Airlines is going to charge for hand luggage .
Frontier Airlines plans to charge up to $100 for carry-on baggage on its flights.
Frontier Airlines plans to introduce a fee of up to $100 for carry-on luggage and $2 for coffee or soda, though in its announcement on Wednesday, it said passengers will be able to keep the entire can.
The new hand luggage charge applies to luggage in the upper luggage compartment, so small baggage under the seat will continue to be free.
