The government side is said to include 29,954 members of Bashar al-Assad's armed forces, 18,678 pro-government fighters and 187 members of Lebanon's Hezbollah.
The death toll also includes 2,202 government defectors and some 5,375 opposition fighters, many of them foreigners.
